OL,3,CNumber of swimming spots failing water
OL,4,Cquality standards double in a year
OL,6,FThe number of official swimming spots
OL,7,Fin England failing water quality
OL,8,Fstandards has risen, ITV News' West of
OL,9,FEngland reporter Sangita Lal reports
OL,11,FThe number of official swimming spots
OL,12,Fin England failing water quality
OL,13,Fstandards has risen to one in 12,
OL,14,Faccording to the latest figures from
OL,15,Fthe UK's environmental regulator.
OL,17,FThe Environment Agency monitored the
OL,18,Fwater quality of 450 sites last year,
OL,19,Fand found 8.2% of them had failed
OL,20,Ftests - leading 37 areas to be
OL,21,Fclassified as "poor".
