OL,6,FMost sites met minimum standards for
OL,7,Fwater quality, with more than 64%
OL,8,Frated "excellent".
OL,10,FTests for harmful bacteria take place
OL,11,Fthroughout the designated swimming
OL,12,Fseason between May and September.
OL,13,FWater quality readings from the past
OL,14,Ffour years are used to classify each
OL,15,Fsite as either excellent, good,
OL,16,Fsufficient or poor.
