OL,6,FThe results also revealed a gap in
OL,7,Fwater quality between sea swimming
OL,8,Fspots and rivers. Some 95% of coastal
OL,9,Fbathing areas met minimum standards,
OL,10,Fwhile only 53% of inland waters were
OL,11,Fclassed as sufficient or better.
OL,13,FTo find out your local swimming site's
OL,14,Fclassification, use the Environment
OL,15,FAgency's Swimfo tool.
OL,17,FWater Minister Emma Hardy said the
OL,18,Fgovernment was working to strengthen
OL,19,Fregulation of the water industry by
OL,20,Fputting companies under special
OL,21,Fmeasures.
