OL,6,FShe said: "These figures are
OL,7,Funacceptable and show that too many of
OL,8,Four popular swimming spots are
OL,9,Fpolluted."
OL,11,FThe latest figures saw 27 newly-
OL,12,Fdesignated bathing waters given a
OL,13,Frating for the first time, leading to
OL,14,Fa slight increase in the number of
OL,15,F"excellent" ratings compared to last
OL,16,Fyear - but the percentage of sites
OL,17,Fmaking the grade has dropped.
