OL,6,FHe said: "The Government's own data
OL,7,Fshows that swimming in our inland
OL,8,Fbathing sites poses serious health
OL,9,Frisks, highlighting the failure of
OL,10,Fregulators to protect waterways from
OL,11,Fpolluters."
OL,13,FGiles Bristow, chief executive of
OL,14,FSurfers Against Sewage, said the
OL,15,Fbathing water classification regime
OL,16,F"isn't just inadequate, it's
OL,17,Fmisleading and needs radical reform".
