OL,6,FHe referred to Trevaunance Cove in
OL,7,FCornwall, which received an excellent
OL,8,Frating in this year's results, but
OL,9,Fwhere community testing had
OL,10,Fhighlighted consistently high levels
OL,11,Fof pollution in a stream running on to
OL,12,Fthe beach.
OL,14,FEnvironment Agency chairman Alan
OL,15,FLovell said they showed there was
OL,16,Fstill more to be done to tackle
OL,17,Fpollution.
