OL,6,F"While overall bathing water quality
OL,7,Fhas improved in recent decades due to
OL,8,Ftargeted investment and robust
OL,9,Fregulation, today's results show there
OL,10,Fis much work still to do, particularly
OL,11,Fto bring our inland bathing waters up
OL,12,Fto standard," he said.
OL,14,F"We are working with the water
OL,15,Findustry, farmers and local
OL,16,Fauthorities and are investing in our
OL,17,Fregulation, with more people on the
OL,18,Fground, updated digital assets and new
OL,19,Flegal powers to improve our bathing
OL,20,Fwaters for all."
